research/history/round_summaries/round_0092.json:37:      "按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 粗估，`factorized_expert_topk K=128 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=16 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 的 total_cost 约 0.31x，明显低于 r86 所在成本带，也落在当前最需要补强的低成本区间。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0092.json:41:      "如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 在约 0.31x total_cost 下显著优于 r86 并接近当前 <0.5x 前沿，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=32`，验证 shared-basis MoE-like 的容量扩张是否继续成立。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0092.json:42:      "如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 有正信号但仍弱于预期，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，区分瓶颈是在 shared basis 宽度还是在 routed capacity。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0092.json:43:      "如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 仍然表现很差，则说明当前 target 上 multi-expert routed-only 路线整体不值得继续，后续应把低成本结构预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert`。"
