research/history/round_summaries/round_0133.json:40:      "如果该点在约 0.21x 下显著优于现有同级低成本 anchor，则下一轮保持 `factorized_expert_topk` 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128`，继续测试 expert-internal low-rank 是否还能进一步左移。",
